  "requires_human_review": true
}
```

### `tests/test_preview.py`

- Extended fallback assertions so the unavailable-preview path keeps
  `approval_state` and `requires_human_review`.
- Added a regression through `build_policy_preview(...)` for the
  `manual_review` normalization case.

